data.description: Beautifully maintained 4-level home with room for expansion in the unfinished basement. Ideally located in the quiet, established neighborhood of Ridgeview at Stetson Hills. Covered front porch to enjoy the Colorado sunshine. Central air and heat for year-round comfort. You’ll enjoy the neutral, peaceful palate in this home. As you enter, you’re greeted by gorgeous LVP floors throughout the main level. The large Living Room features a picture window and stairs to the upper and lower levels. There is a seamless transition to the Dining Area and a pass through into the Kitchen. The Kitchen features pendant lights and white cabinets with ample countertops for kitchen storage and easy food preparation. Stainless steel appliances include a smooth top range oven, built-in microwave, dishwasher, and side by side refrigerator. Walk out to the backyard deck to relax and enjoy outdoor dining. Main-Level Laundry. The Lower-Level includes a Family Room with neutral carpet and a gas log fireplace to cozy up to on chilly winter nights. There is a Bedroom and Shower Bathroom, perfect for guests or in-laws. The Upper-Level offers two Bedrooms, a Full Bathroom, and landing with linen cabinet outside the Primary Bedroom. The Primary Owner’s Suite provides neutral carpet, a lighted ceiling fan, walk in closet, and adjoining Full Bathroom with vanity, mirror, and tub/shower accessed by the Primary Bedroom or hallway. There is a 2-car attached garage with door opener and built-in storage shelves. The Fenced Backyard features an expanded deck that overlooks a level yard for outdoor family fun. This delightful home is conveniently located to all the shopping, restaurants, theatres, and other amenities that the Powers Corridor has to offer. Minutes to Vista Ridge High School. Easy commute to Peterson Space Force Base and the Colorado Springs Airport. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this MOVE-IN READY home your own!
